{"title":"给许志行的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给许志行的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1954年7月25日）志行兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月的信，早已收到，迟复为歉。知你仍在做教育工作，甚为高兴。此复。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺问近安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年七月廿五日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]许志行，1919年冬和毛泽东在汉口相识，当时在上海市格致中学任语文教师。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1954,"month":7,"day":25}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":175,"page_end":175}